{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/airbnb/lottie-android/issues/2125","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/airbnb/lottie-android","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/airbnb/lottie-android/issues/2125/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/airbnb/lottie-android/issues/2125/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/airbnb/lottie-android/issues/2125/events","html_url":"https://github.com/airbnb/lottie-android/issues/2125","id":1359224306,"node_id":"I_kwDOBC8mW85RBB3y","number":2125,"title":"LottieAnimation Composable: support LottieAnimationView (XML) repeatMode equivalent","user":{"login":"brentwatson","id":1331002,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEzMzEwMDI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1331002?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson","html_url":"https://github.com/brentwatson","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":779072574,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWw3NzkwNzI1NzQ=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/airbnb/lottie-android/labels/New%20feature","name":"New feature","color":"5319e7","default":false,"description":null}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":1,"created_at":"2022-09-01T18:09:46Z","updated_at":"2022-10-06T13:54:46Z","closed_at":"2022-10-06T13:54:46Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"`lottie-compose`'s `LottieAnimation` Composable does not support the equivalent of `LottieAnimationView` `app:lottie_repeatMode=reverse|restart` XML attribute.\r\n\r\nIt would be great if `LottieAnimation` were to add something like a `repeatMode: LottieRepeatMode` parameter.\r\n\r\nI've been able to do this manually by switching between a positive and negative animation speeds. But it would be nice if this was supported internally by `LottieAnimation`.\r\n\r\n```kotlin\r\n@Composable\r\nfun LottieAnimationLoopReverse(\r\n    modifier: Modifier = Modifier,\r\n    asset: LottieCompositionSpec.Asset,\r\n) {\r\n    val composition by rememberLottieComposition(asset)\r\n    var shouldReverse by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }\r\n    val lottieAnimation = rememberLottieAnimatable()\r\n    if (shouldReverse) {\r\n        LaunchedEffect(composition) {\r\n            lottieAnimation.animate(composition = composition, speed = -1f)\r\n            shouldReverse = false\r\n        }\r\n    } else {\r\n        LaunchedEffect(composition) {\r\n            lottieAnimation.animate(composition = composition, speed = 1f)\r\n            shouldReverse = true\r\n        }        \r\n    }\r\n\r\n    LottieAnimation(\r\n        composition = composition,\r\n        progress = lottieAnimation.value,\r\n        modifier = modifier,\r\n    )\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"brentwatson","id":1331002,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEzMzEwMDI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1331002?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson","html_url":"https://github.com/brentwatson","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/brentwatson/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/airbnb/lottie-android/issues/2125/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/airbnb/lottie-android/issues/2125/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}